OL,7,FThe son of a music teacher who died
OL,8,Fafter contracting HIV and hepatitis C
OL,9,Ffrom has said he wants to "hear people
OL,10,Fbeing held accountable" as an inquiry
OL,11,Finto the infected blood scandal
OL,12,Fconcludes.
OL,14,FFather-of-two Norman Harris, from
OL,15,FTreorchy, is one of more than 3,000
OL,16,Fvictims to have died after receiving
OL,17,Fcontaminated blood products from the
OL,18,F1970s to the early 1990s. 30,000 NHS
OL,19,Fpatients are thought to have been
OL,20,Finfected in the UK.
