OL,7,FThe chair of the Infected Blood
OL,8,FInquiry, which opened in 2017, is due
OL,9,Fto publish his final report today
OL,10,F(Monday, 20 May).
OL,12,FOwain Harris, who is also a music
OL,13,Fteacher, did not find out about his
OL,14,Ffather's HIV status until he was in
OL,15,Fhis late twenties.
OL,17,FHe said he is still unsure who in his
OL,18,Ffamily knows the truth about what
OL,19,Fhappened to his father, who died aged
OL,20,F65 in 2012.
