OL,3,C'My father's death was not
OL,4,Cinevitable', says son of infected
OL,5,Cblood victim
OL,7,F"(My parents) lived with it and they
OL,8,Fkept it a secret from everybody for
OL,9,Fmany, many years - their own families
OL,10,F- and that must have been tough, that
OL,11,Fmust have been really difficult," he
OL,12,Ftold ITV Cymru Wales.
OL,14,F"At the time I was quite angry, I've
OL,15,Fgot to be honest, because this secret
OL,16,Fhad been kept from myself and my
OL,17,Fsister. I've grown to realise that my
OL,18,Fparents were just protecting me from
OL,19,Fthat stigma.
