OL,7,F"What also frustrates me in all this
OL,8,Fis they had very little support from
OL,9,Fthe NHS in those days about how to
OL,10,Fdeal with this.
OL,12,F"They were never told, ever, how to
OL,13,Ftell their children. They were never
OL,14,Fgiven any support how to tell anybody
OL,15,Felse. They were given very little
OL,16,Fpsychological support."
