OL,7,FIn April 2023, the inquiry recommended
OL,8,Fthat bereaved parents and children
OL,9,Fshould receive #100,000 in
OL,10,Fcompensation, but Owain said he and
OL,11,Fhis sister have not received a penny.
OL,13,FWhen asked whether his father ever
OL,14,Freceived compensation, Owain said:
OL,15,F"Compensation, you would assume, means
OL,16,Fyou get paid something by somebody
OL,17,Fwho's done something wrong. If we're
OL,18,Fdefining compensation as that, the
OL,19,Fanswer is no.
