OL,7,FUntil now, Owain has only spoken to
OL,8,Fclose relatives and friends about his
OL,9,Ffamily's ordeal.
OL,11,F"Going through it in childhood and so
OL,12,Fon was stressful enough, but
OL,13,Fironically having this public inquiry
OL,14,Fgoing on for so long, it has just been
OL,15,Fhanging over us now since 2017 and
OL,16,Fit's now 2024, that's longer than
OL,17,FWorld War II, do you know what I mean?
OL,18,FThat's a long time.
