OL,3,C'My father's death was not
OL,4,Cinevitable', says son of infected
OL,5,Cblood victim
OL,7,F"It's taken its toll and we just want
OL,8,Fit to come to an end and a resolution
OL,9,Fand to draw a line really, and to hear
OL,10,Fpeople being held accountable, just so
OL,11,Fwe've got some sort of closure.
OL,13,F"I want to see exactly what went on,
OL,14,Fwho did what and why. I want to know
OL,15,Fwhy it's been covered up for so long,
OL,16,Fbecause it has, and moving forward
OL,17,Fthat it doesn't happen again."
