OL,7,FMore than 100 people in Wales are
OL,8,Fthought to have died after contracting
OL,9,FHIV or hepatitis C from blood products
OL,10,Fknown as factor VIII.
OL,12,FIt was made by mixing the plasma of up
OL,13,Fto 60,000 people, including high-risk
OL,14,Fgroups like prisoners and drug users
OL,15,Fin the US.
OL,17,F"There were other treatments available
OL,18,Fthat other countries used, it was just
OL,19,Fthe UK went for the cheaper option and
OL,20,Fthat's the sad reality," Owain said.
