OL,7,FOwain said he has been left
OL,8,F"sceptical" of the NHS and distrustful
OL,9,Fof governments as a result of the
OL,10,Fscandal.
OL,12,F"Whenever I or a member of my family
OL,13,Fhas to deal with the NHS, I've got to
OL,14,Fbe honest, I'm always sceptical. I
OL,15,Fbasically end up telling the doctors
OL,16,Fwhat's happened just so they know and
OL,17,Funderstand why I'm asking so many
OL,18,Fquestions about my treatment or
OL,19,Fsomebody else's treatment.
