OL,5,Cblood victim
OL,7,F"It just gives you a mistrust of
OL,8,Fgovernment, but not just government in
OL,9,Fthe sense of politicians, in the sense
OL,10,Fof the establishment and the civil
OL,11,Fservice and how the country is run."
OL,13,FThe UK Government said it has paid
OL,14,Fmore than #400million in interim
OL,15,Fcompensation payments, providing
OL,16,F#100,000 to those infected or bereaved
OL,17,Fpartners registered with the UK
OL,18,FInfected Blood Support Schemes since
OL,19,FOctober 2022.
