OL,7,FThey added: "This includes
OL,8,Festablishing a new body to deliver an
OL,9,FInfected Blood Compensation Scheme,
OL,10,Fconfirming the government will make
OL,11,Fthe required regulations for it within
OL,12,Fthree months of Royal Assent, and that
OL,13,Fit will have all the funding needed to
OL,14,Fdeliver compensation once they have
OL,15,Fidentified the victims and assessed
OL,16,Fclaims.
OL,18,F"In addition, we have included a
OL,19,Fstatutory duty to provide additional
OL,20,Finterim payments to the estates of
OL,21,Fdeceased infected people.
